{"tid":1757254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道指中央深圳設指揮中心應對香港示威　擬撤換王志民","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:42:12.000Z","uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac507bb7a56ac811a43f220c84863a39510285ac","tid":1757254,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">《路透社》引述消息人士報道</span>，為加強管控香港反修例事件引發的動盪，北京在深圳設立危機管理中心，並考慮撤換中聯辦主任王志民。報道引述中國官員指，國家主席習近平每天都從深圳紫荊山莊收到有關香港的書面簡報，又說紫荊山莊已經成為「前線指揮中心」，負責協調和監督香港的局勢。報道又引述知情人士表示，北京對中聯辦處理香港危機不滿意，認為中聯辦誤判香港局勢，和香港市民關係疏離，正考慮撤換中聯辦主任王志民。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-26 10:02:48<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦係咪要正式全面換新疆官員頂住檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5126da401e5f0ef9a8670ee37410f4651e42877a","tid":1757254,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"紫荊山莊2014 本身都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c41ff2b81cd91720918197ccb7e68538af0a57d","tid":1757254,"uid":25797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"成日話誤判形勢 夠薑學Donald Trump咁講叫習近平落嚟親身同前線接觸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abfa4daf214df5a9bd5df439b586a611b8752b7","tid":1757254,"uid":181655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"出曬聲重扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4b3a723f6b0f019a096c50b462675a99608b8d","tid":1757254,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"本身撤